Hi espurious. Big thanks for your weekly gifts! I think that TPB doesn't accept some of your torrents because there are too many files in them. See http://thepiratebay.org/torrent/5177139/R.E.M._-_Discography_%281983_-_2008%29_%5BFLAC%5D_-_Kitlope . Uploader Kitlope solves the problem in this way: "This is a small torrent on how to access the larger 4.91 GB REM - Discography FLAC music torrent. As in the past, the original folder is too big due to the cap TPB has on the amount of files allowed within a torrent. In this small .torrent is the .torrent that you can double click on and will open in your client. Also, theres some links within this small .torrent to a couple other sites where the torrent is posted that, unlike TPB, has no cap."
